⏺ Done! Here's what I built:

  Grid Layout:
  - 6 rows × 10 columns (600×600)
  - Each cell = one decade (1500, 1510, 1520... up to 2020)
  - 2000s row only shows 3 decades (2000, 2010, 2020)
  - Dark theme with subtle decade labels

  25 Historical Events including:
  - Single-decade events (Moon Landing 1960s, 9/11 2000s)
  - Multi-decade spans (Cold War 1940s-1990s, Atlantic Slave Trade
  1500s-1860s, Industrial Revolution 1760s-1840s)

  Animation:
  - Cells flash gold and fade to a dim gold
  - Multi-year events cascade the flash across all decades
  - Randomized order, reshuffles after going through all

