  1. S-Curve (Green) - Tech adoption, learning
  2. Inverted U (Orange) - Stress/performance, drug dosage
  3. Exponential (Red) - Compound interest, viral spread
  4. Power Law (Purple) - Wealth distribution, Zipf
  5. Logarithmic (Cyan) - Perception, Richter scale
  6. J-Curve (Pink) - PE returns, change management
  7. Diminishing Returns (Emerald) - Productivity, utility
  8. Hyperbolic Discounting (Orange) - Procrastination, immediate
  gratification
  9. Bathtub Curve (Indigo) - Failure rates, mortality
  10. Long Tail (Violet) - Netflix, Amazon, niche markets
  11. Step Function (Teal) - Phase transitions, tipping points
  12. Logistic Decay (Rose) - Obsolescence, declining platforms

